author: frogstudio
title: Nice set, specially when it comes for free  :)
review:
Some sort of surgeon (think it's the only way you can get this minifig) with a stretcher and oxygen bottle.  My girlfriend got it for free when she bought me the Viking longship in Hong Kong!

Pros:

Nice Minifig
Stretcher
Printed Tile
Oxygen Bottle


Cons:

None

author: general_veers
title: ok freebie
review:
All this set is is a doctor with a stretcher and an oxygen tank 

Pros-
Doctor
Stretcher
Oxygen tank

Cons- 
Should come with a patient
Stretcher cant move on wheels, as they are just moulded on

Minifigs-
Doctor- OK, he's got a heart monitor printed on his chest, and glasses on his head (where else?)

Get it if-
You want a doctor without paying a bigger price

Dont get it if-
You want a bigger set

Playability- 5/10 
Minifigs- 7/10
Price- 8/10
Design- 7/10
Accuracy- 7/10
Construction- 6/10
Overall- 6/10

author: hustla187
title: One of the Best Promos
review: I really like this promo because this has some cool stuff like a stretcher, a nitrous oxide tank, and a doctor minifig. It is perfect if you don't have much of any of the hospital sets. Overall, this is very good.

author: Alemas
title: I've got two of these!
review:
This is a nice little set, with a doctor, stretcher, suitcase, and a bottle of what looks like anaesthetic!

Pros:

Stretcher
Doctor
Suitcase
Bottle of anaesthetic

Cons:

None!

Overall, a nice set!
